{"id":23214,"date":"2022-12-20T08:46:05","date_gmt":"2022-12-20T07:46:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/?page_id=23214"},"modified":"2024-10-01T11:30:17","modified_gmt":"2024-10-01T09:30:17","slug":"professional-development-programme","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/en\/career\/working-at-mannheimer-swartling\/professional-development-programme\/","title":{"rendered":"Professional Development Programme"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"preamble\">The Professional Development Programme (PDP) covers your first six years at the firm. The programme includes training in specific legal topics, along with other areas such as business management, legal English, negotiating techniques, professional ethics, rhetoric, digital tools and entrepreneurship.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-26120 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-778-1200x800.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-778-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-778-2000x1334.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-778-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-778-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-778-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/11\/01-corporate-msa-gbg-778-2048x1366.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The PDP enables you to develop your legal skills and understanding of our clients\u2019 businesses. The first two years of the programme give you a thorough understanding of the firm\u2019s approach to substantive law 